{"tid":2215472,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"「楊明效應」寶馬逆線上橋迎撼3車 司機涉拒提供血液樣本被捕","createTime":"2020-09-24T04:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T06:50:40.000Z","uid":34147,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"84ca34ddc15ff9cc298305c457ec8023fa03baa3","tid":2215472,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200924/bkn-20200924050917935-0924_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200924%2Fbkn-20200924050917935-0924_00822_001.html&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=bdfbf949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200924/bkn-20200924050917935-0924_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200924/photo/bkn-20200924050917935-0924_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200924121613\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200924%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200924050917935-0924_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200924121613&h=ca3c060f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉事寶馬司機意外後疑不支倒地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日（24日）凌晨4時許，一輛寶馬房車在灣仔堅拿道東天橋逆線上橋行駛，至銅鑼灣伊利莎伯大廈對開，與迎頭而至的一輛貨車及兩輛私家車相撞。涉事房車車頭損毀，安全氣袋彈出，姓姚(45歲)寶馬男司機疑體力不支倒地。<br />\n警方接報到場，為姚進行酒精呼氣測試，證實他體內酒精含量超標，其後涉嫌「拒絕提供血液樣本」被捕，他報稱不適送院治理。<br />\n意外中兩名分別姓何(35歲)及姓黃(40歲)私家車男司機及姓張(34歲)貨車男司機亦分別因頸痛及腰痛，由救護車送往律敦治醫院治理。<br />\n <br />\n笑撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/l6an2EQiMQ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl6an2EQiMQ0&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=2b0372dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l6an2EQiMQ0</a>"},{"pid":"6910ffb53e1dcb931f4e68d516cd2f973ca92925","tid":2215472,"uid":100623,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"呀～～屌你老母...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bed80293f1bfb7f88ef8079d1fadac2013568ab","tid":2215472,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:36:03.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"21ecbb12f92a1c0d795f1280d0cd15e1c5529449","tid":2215472,"uid":94591,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"楊明效應 楊明唱 楊明高溫作出呼應"},{"pid":"204ae0a3027a98217f0c0cb2289b042f7084d761","tid":2215472,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"醉酒駕駛 累己累人"},{"pid":"32164e696655fde8c1983e711f8b148a8b8d281c","tid":2215472,"uid":367093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:40:46.000Z","msg":"姚(被捕)：咩jerk，楊明拒絕又冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb0b5fe3d39f8ae88d753960c330b7edaf01776","tid":2215472,"uid":87172,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"其實拒絕提供仲罸得重過超標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ea6a205bf90a2d21bd71368652778c6547876c","tid":2215472,"uid":45660,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"大聲話自己係藍屍<br />\n撞到個班就全黃<br />\n咁就咩事都冇"},{"pid":"b591ca67ebc24af914eec06b795ea4d49fe6ca36","tid":2215472,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bb0b5fe3d39f8ae88d753960c330b7edaf01776","tid":2215472,"uid":87172,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"其實拒絕提供仲罸得重過超標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"睇個官判"},{"pid":"4f85fde55c63c0f51fbed84704c6e5358a55908d","tid":2215472,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"警犬做野唔使你教"},{"pid":"4b80be6632c